Package comp3110.mechanismsDomain

Class EventInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • comp3110.mechanismsDomain.EventInstance
  • public class EventInstance
extends java.lang.Object
    All events generated during the execution of an application are implemented as instances of the EventInstance Java class. This class is not often used directly by the programmer.
